---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Versioning"
  description="Learn about Open Cleaner RN's versioning strategy, release process, and development workflow using semantic versioning and automated CI/CD."
>
  <Navigation />
  
  <main>
		<h1>Versioning and Release Process</h1>
		
		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Version Numbering</h2>
			<p>
				We follow Semantic Versioning (SemVer) for our releases:
			</p>
			<pre><code>MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH</code></pre>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>MAJOR</strong>: Incompatible API changes</li>
				<li><strong>MINOR</strong>: New features (backwards-compatible)</li>
				<li><strong>PATCH</strong>: Bug fixes (backwards-compatible)</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Automated Release Process</h2>
			<p>
				Our release process is fully automated using GitHub Actions. Here's how it works:
			</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Create and push a new tag:
					<pre><code>git tag -a v1.0.0 -m "Release v1.0.0"
git push origin v1.0.0</code></pre>
				</li>
				<li>The GitHub Action workflow automatically:
					<ul>
						<li>Builds the application for all platforms (Windows, macOS, Linux)</li>
						<li>Creates platform-specific packages</li>
						<li>Generates a GitHub Release</li>
						<li>Uploads all artifacts</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ol>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Available Platforms</h2>
			<p>We automatically build and package for:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Windows</strong>: MSI installer</li>
				<li><strong>macOS</strong>: DMG package</li>
				<li><strong>Linux</strong>: AppImage, DEB, and RPM packages</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Release Channels</h2>
			<table>
				<thead>
					<tr>
						<th>Channel</th>
						<th>Description</th>
						<th>Version Pattern</th>
					</tr>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td>Stable</td>
						<td>Production-ready releases</td>
						<td>v1.0.0</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>Beta</td>
						<td>Pre-release testing</td>
						<td>v1.0.0-beta.1</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td>Alpha</td>
						<td>Early testing</td>
						<td>v1.0.0-alpha.1</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Development Workflow</h2>
			<ol>
				<li>Development happens on feature branches</li>
				<li>Features are merged into the <code>dev</code> branch</li>
				<li>Release candidates are created from <code>dev</code></li>
				<li>After testing, releases are merged into <code>main</code></li>
				<li>Tags are created on <code>main</code> for releases</li>
			</ol>
		</section>

		<section class="content-section">
			<h2>Automatic Updates</h2>
			<p>
				The application checks for updates automatically and can self-update on all platforms.
				Updates are signed and verified for security.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
		max-width: 900px;
	}
	
	/* Page Hero */
	.page-hero {
		padding: 3rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	[data-theme="dark"] .page-hero {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #374151 100%);
	}
	
	h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}
	.content-section {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background-color: #23262d;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	h2 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	pre {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		overflow-x: auto;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}
	code {
		font-family: monospace;
		white-space: pre;
	}
	ul, ol {
		margin-left: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	li {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}
	strong {
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	table {
		width: 100%;
		border-collapse: collapse;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}
	th, td {
		padding: 0.75rem;
		text-align: left;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}
	th {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	tr:nth-child(even) {
		background-color: #1a1a1a;
	}
</style> 